Subject: [PATCH v4 2/2] SMAF: add CMA allocator
Date: Mon,  5 Oct 2015 12:11:38 +0200
Message-Id: <1444039898-7927-3-git-send-email-benjamin.gaignard@linaro.org>
In-Reply-To: <1444039898-7927-1-git-send-email-benjamin.gaignard@linaro.org>
